V0301_01_00_00_0.text:
Fine.
I have a few minutes to spare.

V0301_01_00_01_0.text: I will destroy you until there's nothing left of you!

V0301_01_00_02_1.text: You'll regret challenging me to a Duel.

V0301_01_00_03_0.text: Whatever your reason for Dueling me...

V0301_01_00_03_1.text: You better not waste my time by holding back!

V0301_01_00_04_0.text: I’ve been waiting for this for a long time, Pharaoh!

V0301_01_00_04_1.text:
Prepare to do battle!
And prepare to lose!

V0301_01_00_05_0.text: You’re the closest I’ve ever had to a worthy adversary.

V0301_01_00_06_0.text:
Let's Duel!
Even if you're not the real Pharaoh!

V0301_01_00_07_0.text:
Yugi, you will Duel me.
This matter is not up for debate.

V0301_01_00_08_0.text: Yugi, you're nothing more than a useless vessel!

V0301_01_00_09_0.text: You'll learn the hard way, you're still not in my league!

V0301_01_00_10_0.text:
Mokuba!
Don't expect me to go easy on you!

V0301_01_00_11_0.text: Diva, it's time to end this!

V0301_01_00_12_0.text:
Aigami...
Or shall I call you Diva.

V0301_01_00_12_1.text: Whatever your name is, one thing is certain: Your defeat!

V0301_01_00_13_0.text: I'll defeat you in this dimension or any dimension!

V0301_01_00_14_0.text: You think I'll give in to fear?

V0301_01_00_14_1.text:
I fear nothing!
Especially not you!

V0301_01_00_15_1.text: Then let's see if you can remake your defeat into victory!

V0301_03_00_00_0.text: It's time to bring this Duel to an end.

V0301_06_01_01_0.text: You have to try harder than that!

V0301_07_09_01_0.text: I flip over my Set card!

V0301_08_00_01_0.text:
So what!
I activate my Trap, Induced Explosion!

V0301_08_00_02_0.text: I banish Induced Explosion to destroy your card!

V0301_08_00_03_0.text:
I activate my Trap, Dark Sacrifice!
Your effect is negated!

V0301_08_00_03_1.text: And I send a monster from my deck to my Graveyard!

V0301_08_00_04_0.text:
I activate my Trap!
Counter Gate!

V0301_08_00_04_1.text: Your attack is negated, and I draw a card!

V0301_08_00_05_1.text: My Dragon gains an attack for each Special Summoned monster!

V0301_08_00_06_0.text: Don't you know you've already lost?

V0301_08_00_07_0.text:
I'll activate this card!
Monster Reborn!

V0301_08_00_08_0.text:
Here's my Trap Monster!
Krystal Avatar!

V0301_08_00_09_0.text: When it's destroyed, you take damage equal to its ATK!

V0301_08_00_10_0.text: I can use this Spell Card to summon higher Level monsters!

V0301_08_00_11_0.text:
I activate my Spell Card!
The Flute of Summoning Dragon!

V0301_08_00_11_1.text: By playing this flute,  Lord of D. Special Summons a Dragon!

V0301_08_00_12_0.text:
The Quick-Play Spell, Shrink!
It halves a monster's ATK!

V0301_08_00_13_0.text: Even the cards know which Duelist should win!

V0301_08_00_13_1.text: I activate the Spell Card, Lullaby of Obedience!

V0301_08_00_14_0.text:
I activate my Spell Card!
Card of Demise!

V0301_08_00_15_0.text: I activate my Spell Card, Silent Doom!

V0301_08_00_16_0.text: The Quick-Play Spell, Rage with Eyes of Blue!

V0301_08_00_16_1.text: I banish my hand, field and Graveyard to summon Blue-Eyes!

V0301_08_00_17_0.text: With this, Blue-Eyes Ultimate Dragon can attack three times!

V0301_08_00_17_1.text: And you can't activate effects during these attacks!

V0301_08_00_18_0.text: The Spell Card, Bingo Machine, Go!!!!

V0301_08_00_18_1.text: I add the card you choose to my hand!

V0301_08_00_19_0.text:
I activate my Spell Card!
Burst Stream of Destruction!

V0301_08_00_20_0.text: My Blue-Eyes will paralyze anyone with its glare!

V0301_08_00_20_1.text: The Quick-Play Spell, Majesty with Eyes of Blue!

V0301_08_00_21_0.text: I equip Beacon of White on Blue-Eyes to Special Summon it!

V0301_08_00_22_0.text:
I now activate my Trap!
Cloning!

V0301_08_00_23_0.text:
I activate my Trap!
Interdimensional Matter Transporter!

V0301_08_00_24_0.text: Heh! You think you can avoid a fight?

V0301_08_00_24_1.text:
I activate my Continuous Trap!
Final Attack Orders!

V0301_08_00_25_0.text: I'll rip the wings off your strategy!

V0301_08_00_25_1.text:
I activate my virus card!
Virus Cannon!

V0301_08_00_26_0.text: With this Trap, my Blue-Eyes becomes...

V0301_08_00_27_0.text: I activate a Trap from my Graveyard!

V0301_08_00_27_1.text: I Set this card on my field!

V0301_08_00_28_0.text:
I activate my Spell Card!
The Melody of Awakening Dragon!

V0301_08_00_29_0.text:
I activate my Spell Card!
Dragon Revival Rhapsody!

V0301_09_00_00_0.text: I use Assault Wyvern's effect to call forth this monster!

V0301_09_00_01_0.text: By destroying your monster, this card gains ATK!

V0301_09_00_02_0.text: By destroying this card, your monster loses ATK!

V0301_09_00_03_0.text: Since it battled, I'll add this card in my deck to my hand!

V0301_09_00_04_0.text: Its effect lets me use LP to lower a monster's ATK!

V0301_09_00_05_0.text: Pandemic Dragon destroys a monster with equal or less ATK!

V0301_09_00_06_0.text: When Pandemic Dragon is destroyed, monsters lose ATK!

V0301_09_00_07_0.text: Blue-Eyes Alternative White Dragon can destroy your monster!

V0301_09_00_08_0.text: Blue-Eyes Twin Burst Dragon banishes your monster!

V0301_09_00_09_0.text: Neo Blue-Eyes Ultimate Dragon can attack three times!

V0301_09_00_10_0.text: I banish Neo Blue-Eyes from the Grave to protect Blue-Eyes!

V0301_09_00_11_0.text: Blue-Eyes Alternative Ultimate Dragon destroys your card!

V0301_09_00_12_0.text: I used Blue-Eyes to Ritual Summon, so it can use its effect!

V0301_09_00_13_0.text: Chaos MAX Dragon deals double piercing damage!

V0301_09_00_14_0.text: This Dragon will make you feel the fury of my other Dragons!

V0301_09_00_15_0.text:
Deep-Eyes!
Inherit the power of the Dragon in my Graveyard!

V0301_09_00_16_0.text: I'm taking your monsters down with it!

V0301_09_00_17_0.text:
Obelisk!
Destroy my monsters to destroy theirs!

V0301_09_00_18_0.text:
A God can only resurrect for one turn.
Return to the earth!

V0301_09_00_30_0.text: Dragon Spirit of White's effect activates!

V0301_09_00_31_0.text: I now negate your monster's effects!

V0301_09_00_32_0.text: I return Solid Dragon to my deck to bring a new Blue-Eyes!

V0301_09_00_33_0.text: I discard a card to activate The King of D.'s effect!

V0301_11_01_00_0.text: I Summon a monster in Defense Position!

V0301_13_00_03_0.text: As long as this is in play, effects can't target Dragons!

V0301_13_00_08_0.text: The light from my dragon erases the shadows!

V0301_13_00_09_0.text: The souls of my Dragons guide a new one to me!

V0301_13_00_09_1.text:
Come on out!
Blue-Eyes Alternative White Dragon!

V0301_13_00_10_0.text:
Show yourself!
Blue-Eyes Twin Burst Dragon!

V0301_37_00_00_0.text: I merge my three Blue-Eyes together!

V0301_37_00_01_0.text:
There's no preparing for this!
I Fusion Summon!

V0301_37_00_02_0.text:
My Ultimate Dragon takes on a new form!
I Fusion Summon!

V0301_13_00_13_0.text:
Come here!
Blue-Eyes Alternative Ultimate Dragon!

V0301_13_00_15_0.text:
Come on out!
Blue-Eyes Chaos MAX Dragon!

V0301_37_00_03_0.text: Watch as the relentless arrives, seeking vengeance!

V0301_13_00_17_0.text:
It's no monster...
It's a god!

V0301_13_00_21_0.text:
X and Y! Combine!
XY-Dragon Cannon!

V0301_13_00_22_0.text: X and Z combines into XZ-Tank Cannon!

V0301_13_00_23_0.text:
Combine, Y and Z!
YZ-Tank Dragon!

V0301_13_00_24_0.text:
X, Y and Z! Combine into one!
XYZ-Dragon Cannon!

V0301_13_00_28_0.text: A, B and C combine into ABC-Dragon Buster!

V0301_13_00_29_0.text: A thru Z join together into A-to-Z-Dragon Buster Cannon!

V0301_14_00_01_0.text: You'll see how much stronger I am than you!

V0301_18_00_00_0.text:
Get out of my sight!
I attack you directly!

V0301_19_00_07_0.text: Unleash your rage, Blue-Eyes Alternative White Dragon!

V0301_19_00_08_0.text:
Blue-Eyes Twin Burst Dragon!
Burn everything down!

V0301_19_00_12_0.text:
Take this!
Blue-Eyes Chaos Dragon! Attack!

V0301_19_00_13_0.text: Put an end to this farce!

V0301_19_00_14_0.text:
It's curtains for you!
Deep-Eyes White Dragon! Attack!

V0301_19_00_22_0.text: This will blast you into shreds!

V0301_19_00_29_0.text:
Take this!
Blue-Eyes Solid Dragon! Attack!

V0301_21_00_01_1.text: Now let's see what you can do!

V0301_21_00_05_0.text: I've had enough of your tricks...

V0301_28_00_00_0.text: A win is a win, but there's someone else I'd rather defeat.

V0301_28_00_02_0.text: I wanted a challenge, but all I got was disappointment.

V0301_28_00_03_1.text: Until I get my rematch with the Pharaoh!

V0301_28_00_04_0.text: It wasn’t the real Pharaoh, so I didn’t really beat him.

V0301_28_00_04_1.text: And until I do, my scars of defeat will continue to burn!

V0301_28_00_05_0.text: You're not the one I want to defeat, Yugi.

V0301_28_00_06_0.text: Your only duty is to bring the Pharaoh’s spirit back!

V0301_28_00_07_0.text: The only Duelist you'll ever beat is the one in the mirror!

V0301_28_00_08_0.text: That was giving it your all, Mokuba?

V0301_28_00_09_0.text: You think your parlor tricks would work against Seto Kaiba?

V0301_28_00_10_0.text: Get in my way and get crushed!

V0301_28_00_11_0.text: Whatever powers you claim to have couldn't stop me!

V0301_28_00_12_0.text: You're a copy as weak as the original.

V0301_28_00_13_1.text: You think I'd feel joy in defeating a replica?

V0301_29_00_01_0.text: You dare interfere with my plans?

V0301_29_00_03_0.text:
How could I lose...
This is unacceptable!

V0301_29_00_05_0.text: Seems I recreated the Pharaoh's deck to be stronger than in real life.

V0301_29_00_06_0.text: Looks like you're a Duelist in your own right, Yugi.

V0301_29_00_07_0.text: I can't believe I have to accept that you're a Duelist...

V0301_29_00_10_0.text: So this is the power of the Plana...

V0301_29_00_11_0.text: I let a copy defeat me?

V0301_30_00_00_0.text: You're simply a pawn in my plan.

V0301_30_00_01_0.text: Let me give you some advice - try not to be so predictable.

V0301_34_00_00_0.text: You want this Duel Disk? Well, you can't have it!

V0301_34_00_02_0.text: My network of security tech lets me know everything.

V0301_34_00_03_0.text: You have what it takes to be a Duelist.

V0301_34_00_05_0.text: You can't hide from me, Pharaoh!

V0301_34_00_06_0.text: Here I go! And I won't be stopped!

V0301_34_00_08_0.text: You don't need to flatter me.

V0301_34_00_09_0.text: Your Dueling never ceases to surprise me.

V0301_32_00_00_0.text:
Yu-Gi-Oh! Duel Links
Unite for the love of Dueling!

V0301_32_00_01_0.text:
Yu-Gi-Oh! Duel Links!
Where I will rule as king!

V0301_36_00_05_0.text: If we're going down, it won’t be without a fight.

V0301_36_00_08_0.text: Where's your bond of friendship to help you now, Yugi?

V0301_36_00_09_0.text: Finish this Duel for me, Mokuba.

V0301_41_00_00_0.text: If this is your dimension, I'll step all over it!
